{"tid":1244766,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[明報] 站係激進派立場個邊，我就真係覺得胡志偉(泛民)又準備割蓆啦","createTime":"2019-06-20T05:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T05:21:07.000Z","uid":37759,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4bbb68cdc7239aeb83f641f9d131c490d84b5dc","tid":1244766,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190620/s00001/1561001169827/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A3%9C%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%92%95%E8%A3%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190620%2Fs00001%2F1561001169827%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25A3%2582&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbAuBxQMtbc6xR8MkqxZcasw%3D&h=b6150a1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190620%2Fs00001%2F1561001169827%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%2583%25A1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2592%25A4%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258E%25A7%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%2595%25E8%25A3%2582&h=de7ffe32\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190620/s00001/1561001169827/%E3%80%90%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E3%80%91%E8%83%A1%E5%BF%97%E5%81%89%E5%80%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%92%A4%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA-%E4%BF%AE%E8%A3%9C%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%92%95%E8%A3%82</a><br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》修訂引發6．12警民衝突，民主黨主席、立法會議員胡志偉今早（20日）在商台節目表示，若政府想與社會重新接軌，處理今次事件應情理兼備，例如撤銷示威者控罪及停止搜捕，有助修補社會撕裂。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">胡志偉認為，正如警務處長盧偉聰所說，絕大部分示威者都是和平，從政治上考慮，政府若以緩和寬鬆的方法處理今次事件，撤銷所有示威者控罪、停止搜查，可為政府與社會重新接軌（reconnect）的起步點；<ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">若因涉嫌扔磚等行為被捕，警方可改控普通襲擊等罪名</span></ins>。</span><br />\n<br />\n出席同一節目的民陣召集人岑子杰表示，要求成立獨立調查委員會，是因為監警會已不能制衡警員，現行機制存在缺陷，才容讓上周三（12日）在場指揮官可下令肆無忌憚向示威市民開槍；獨立調查委員會可令警權得到合理的約制。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如何看香港未來10天局勢發展，岑子杰稱很難評估，現時立法會要監察政府很困難，政府必須自律自制，批評特首林鄭月娥冷處理手法不能平息市民憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大專學界將今午5時設定為死線，要求政府回應訴求。岑子杰表示，民陣今次的角色是參與者，是公民社會的一部分，又說民陣在自己招牌下有其難處。"},{"pid":"b1830a19939963fdf9108c595c15b9ac02c6ad08","tid":1244766,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:17:59.000Z","msg":"鵪鶉党好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08045f944097c428081db0d2535991fc995b653","tid":1244766,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"621 醜事傳千里，輿論救義士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1244725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1244725</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n新部署，入嚟討論"}]}